      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a \"feeling\" tho. it's like the actual substance of who i am is gone. when the art died, the person died too. i'm just a ghost haunting my own life. i look in the mirror and i don't even see a human being, just this meat-suit that keeps moving because it hasn't realized there's no one left inside to drive it. it feels so heavy and pointless.",
